Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:39.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is you, Kirino!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.32,0:01:42.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.65,0:01:44.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.96,0:01:47.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fancy running into you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.66,0:01:50.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... what a coincidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.41,0:01:52.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone she knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:54.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Her best friend, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.72,0:01:56.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.57,0:01:59.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you were taking the day off from work because you were busy with the track team...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:01.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.52,0:02:05.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You want {\i1}me{\i0} to deal with this??
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.34,0:02:11.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:13.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Onii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.06,0:02:17.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Might you two be out on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:19.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.36,0:02:21.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.15,0:02:23.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And what are you up to here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:25.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing a photo shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.93,0:02:27.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now I'm on break.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:31.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Aragaki—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.53,0:02:33.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can just call me Ayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.14,0:02:34.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Ayase-chan then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.72,0:02:36.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in a bit of a hurry right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:38.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirino? Are you feeling okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.86,0:02:41.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kind of quiet, and you look stressed...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.38,0:02:43.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, I'm a bit under the weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.54,0:02:45.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about I have someone drive you back?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.15,0:02:45.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take your bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:48.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, but I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:50.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:54.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for interrupting your date.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.72,0:03:03.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I've been wondering, but do you know those people behind you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:06.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:08.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:11.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't hurry, we'll miss the 5pm anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:19.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry guys... thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:21.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What was with those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:23.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They looked really strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:25.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:28.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know those weirdos.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:33.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, was something going on today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:35.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:37.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably Summer Comiket.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:38.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer Comiket?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:40.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:45.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure myself, but they sell doujinshi and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:47.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Doujinshi"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:49.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:50.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirino...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:52.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hiding something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:54.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:56.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, we'll catch you another time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:03:59.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, Ayase!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:03:59.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:02.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:05.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you running away, Kirino?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.30,0:04:08.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not running...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:09.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:11.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:13.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lies, lies, lies, lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.41,0:04:14.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.07,0:04:16.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You tried to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:17.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:19.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're running!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:20.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase? This—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:23.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You be quiet, Onii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.06,0:04:25.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking with Kirino.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:27.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:35.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirino, I'm worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.49,0:04:37.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So please answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:39.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hiding something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:41.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not, Ayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:43.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:45.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You should know by now, Kirino.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:48.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.28,0:04:51.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not telling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:55.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to talk to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:04:58.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm shocked. And here I thought we were friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:00.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that I misunderstood things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:02.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:04.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:10.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help you, Kirino.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:15.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Something feels wrong today, and I can't just let you go...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.78,0:05:20.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's in that bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:24.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Comic Circle Market"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:30.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going? I'm not done talk—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:50.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:54.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can no longer be your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:56.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't talk to me at school anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:13.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know those weirdos.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:17.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think Miss Kiririn was being serious there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:18.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:22.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are such unfortunate animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:28.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for that back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:30.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, we managed to work it out somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:33.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for using you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.23,0:06:37.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried calling Miss Kiririn too, but she didn't pick up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.63,0:06:39.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She was pretty tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.65,0:06:41.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's already gone to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.12,0:06:43.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed? That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:46.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kuroneko was also quite worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:48.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry again about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.08,0:06:50.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get her to apologize to her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.21,0:06:52.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You needn't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:54.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a lot for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.65,0:06:55.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:08.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best at training camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:10.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.23,0:07:12.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think I am, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:14.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:23.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:28.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When she uses her tentacles, Reika's back becomes exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:31.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't get me wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.77,0:07:34.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I looked this up for you or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:52.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,On your marks...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:53.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Get set...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:54.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:06.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You win!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.14,0:08:11.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can fight against other players!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.16,0:08:25.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:36.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:40.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can use my character against other players now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:41.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:56.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Something happen to you at school today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:57.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:09:00.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Ayase break her promise and tell everyone about your hobby?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.98,0:09:02.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase wouldn't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:07.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you made up with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.14,0:09:11.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:12.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't say anything, I can't help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:14.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.88,0:09:15.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.71,0:09:19.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I talk to you a little and now you're acting all gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.04,0:09:21.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And what's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:22.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:26.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I don't care if I'm gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:32.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I'm a perverted siscon idiot of a brother that thinks he's got something good going on after he got to know his sister a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.56,0:09:35.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not letting you leave here till you tell me the whole story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.31,0:09:37.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:39.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't made up with Ayase, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:42.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:44.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.78,0:09:48.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you acted like nothing happened the day after.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:53.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I had training camp, so I couldn't disappoint anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:54.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:10:04.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of people wanted to go to camp, and since I was chosen to go, I couldn't just stay depressed and not work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:07.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a separate problem, and at the camp I had to focus on doing what I had to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:09.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.18,0:10:12.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So didn't you try calling her or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:16.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:18.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I can help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:20.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she your best friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.56,0:10:22.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really just going to leave things like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:23.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:23.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.03,0:10:27.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking like you know what I'm going through!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:27.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.87,0:10:31.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand the way you're just giving up like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:33.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:38.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally you'd try to fix it any way you could, no matter how unsightly or how low the odds were!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:39.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.65,0:10:41.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you acting all mature all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:44.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting a lecture from you after this long really pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:47.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm not going to sit and listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:51.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to just nod and do what you say, like Neighbor-girl does.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:52.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:53.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:59.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never cared about me my whole life, and only now you're trying to act the big brother part?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.46,0:11:02.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:04.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:08.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I can't leave it like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:09.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:10.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:12.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:12.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to fix it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:14.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it like it's so simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:16.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:17.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:18.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:29.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The life counseling isn't over...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:34.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Take responsibility for it till the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:37.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just say that from the start next time, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:40.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I must refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.14,0:11:44.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot associate myself with someone with that kind of hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:45.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.77,0:11:47.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask you instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.21,0:11:49.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:51.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, the answer's obvious at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:52.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, hold—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:54.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:55.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirino isn't that kind of person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:11:57.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I said hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:11:58.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:02.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say to Kirino today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:05.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a futile effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:09.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was her best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:13.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it natural that I'd want to make up with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:14.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:16.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So I said to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:21.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Drop that hobby and throw it all away."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:24.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what she said?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:26.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She told me, "Never!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:30.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That means that hobby is more important to her than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:31.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:39.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not trying to defend her hobby, but you don't really understand what kind of hobby it is, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:42.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've decided you hate it without really knowing anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.56,0:12:45.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen it on the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:51.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Games and anime where people do lewd things to little girls are becoming more and more widespread in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:55.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A famous journalist reported on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.43,0:12:57.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't those the kind of things Kirino has?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:01.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.95,0:13:08.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So when I find out that my best friend has such a disgusting hobby, isn't it natural for me to try to make her stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:10.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That journalist also said...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:16.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,People who play and watch those things will eventually have their minds broken, and lose their humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:18.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an exaggeration.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.34,0:13:23.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And there was a man who was influenced by those games to electrocute a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:32.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit was one of those so-called otaku would-be-criminals, and he said he was trying to mimic what he saw in a game called "Siscalypse".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:34.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:38.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Those kinds of games and manga shouldn't be allowed to exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.32,0:13:42.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who plays them or creates them is a criminal just waiting to come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.51,0:13:44.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They need to be regulated and controlled!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:48.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a hobby that Kirino absolutely cannot have!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:14:00.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So I guess she's seriously worried about Kirino...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.33,0:14:07.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be hard to deal with how all these incidents involving otaku really do strengthen her argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:17.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Dad, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:20.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What, about your future?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:21.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:27.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A middle school girl I'm friends with recently saw a big haul of eromanga I got!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:28.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:32.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You okay, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.94,0:14:34.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You worthless son!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:38.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You came to me to discuss that, of all things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:40.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to know something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:42.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Just hear me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.39,0:14:45.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:48.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:57.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't make up with Kirino because her hobby is indecent, and she won't give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:14:58.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:15:01.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. And so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:06.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After we talked about that, I looked into a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.81,0:15:09.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have heard about that case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:13.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,An associate of mine at the station brought me the information.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:17.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And I also know about the journalist that wrote the article.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:19.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just happened to be looking into the incident at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:21.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:24.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I looked into it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:26.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start from my results.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:34.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,At first, the culprit in the SisCaly incident did say he tried to electrocute a little girl in imitation of a game,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.63,0:15:36.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but he withdrew that statement later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.44,0:15:38.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:39.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.84,0:15:44.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that he took out the stun gun because he wanted to get violent on a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:46.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pretty sleazy way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:48.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you discover that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:50.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was on the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:52.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The second article was a lot smaller than the first, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:15:55.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But then the journalist would have—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.09,0:15:57.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He published this apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:05.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"I apologize for stating something which may have caused a misunderstanding. I made a mistake in collecting information."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.73,0:16:13.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"I hope to inform you all of the truth with regards to the incident as the time calls."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:16.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't say anything about that on TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:19.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think everything they say is a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:22.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think all the otaku bashing is completely untruthful either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.86,0:16:30.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But as far as this incident goes, I think that journalist may have just misinterpreted some of the information.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:33.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And part of the mass media jumped right on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:35.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more of it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:36.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Read it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:42.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lies! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:46.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's no evidence that playing games causes people to lose their humanity either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.05,0:16:50.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So could you stop referring to otaku as criminals waiting to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:55.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, there might be some bad guys among them, but they aren't all bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:58.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirino said the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.30,0:17:00.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:04.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This was a mistake on my part. I take back what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:09.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't change the fact that Kirino's hobby is disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:13.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You might see it that way, but can't you try to ignore it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:18.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She keeps it to herself because she knows that she can't let anyone know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:20.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:22.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's kept it to herself and lied to us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:25.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She just never had to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:28.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And more importantly, because she didn't want to lose your friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:31.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're her best friend! Why can't you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:34.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you? What do you know about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.31,0:17:36.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know Kirino better than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:38.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That Kirino is fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:41.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Give her back! Give me back my best friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:43.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me back the real Kirino!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:45.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:49.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fake, fake"...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.12,0:17:51.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you say anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:54.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirino...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:17:56.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:59.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is something I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.08,0:18:03.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:07.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not listening to a fake Kirino.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.03,0:18:09.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to talk to the real Kirino!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:11.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the real me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:15.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful, overflowing with style and fashion sense, ace athlete, honor student,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.91,0:18:18.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,surrounded by friends, the idol of the entire student body,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.83,0:18:21.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,loved by the teachers, the star of the track team,{FOTC: Synchronize with first few lines.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:23.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,working as a model outside school,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.94,0:18:26.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,depended on by everyone, loved by everyone—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:31.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,that super-perfect, super-cool, super-cute, super-beautiful Kousaka Kirino? {aww, missing the kyousuke tsukkomi}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:32.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the real me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:34.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That's Kirino!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:37.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry Ayase, but you don't really understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.44,0:18:42.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I like the manga that you call indecent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.42,0:18:44.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I really like those eroge you call disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:48.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I never get tired of watching anime with cute girls no matter how many times I watch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:51.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I get really happy just looking at my character goods!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.35,0:18:53.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I really like those things!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can even say I love them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.81,0:18:58.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what anyone says, that's who I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:03.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So I know you're worried about me, but I won't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.25,0:19:05.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't throw away this hobby no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:07.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:08.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I like what I like!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:11.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I stop, I won't be me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:13.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it more important than your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:16.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your hobby more important than me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:18.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:21.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you just as much as my eroge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.19,0:19:22.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:24.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were able to just pick one, I wouldn't have any problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.74,0:19:27.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I love both my friends and my eroge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:31.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Things turned out like this because I love them both!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:36.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't plan on throwing away either of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:37.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I need both.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:38.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So I've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:40.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am going to make up with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:42.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will not throw away my hobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:44.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:49.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.73,0:19:52.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You love me a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.03,0:19:57.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:20:00.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make up with you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:05.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't accept your hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:06.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:08.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:10.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:12.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you just say you'd make up with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:17.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I can't stand that kind of manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:19.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:21.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirino!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.16,0:20:23.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.69,0:20:26.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You want me to step in {\i1}now{\i0}??
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:28.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirino, what should I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:30.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.35,0:20:39.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:40.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:42.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:51.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:52.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat you to a pulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.24,0:20:53.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Filthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:55.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That right there...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.39,0:20:58.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,is the symbol of love between me and Kirino!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:01.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-wha-wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.36,0:21:03.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of crazy talk are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:06.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We in love with each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:09.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we've been gathering tales of forbidden love!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.55,0:21:15.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't found that, I would never have realized my feelings for Kirino.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:19.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Our relationship would have been frozen over forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.29,0:21:24.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirino's hobby has repaired the bonds between us that were broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.30,0:21:28.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We were able to become true siblings through it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:32.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You think we'd let anyone deny these feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.78,0:21:34.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, and listen well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.40,0:21:35.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.31,0:21:36.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.86,0:21:37.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:42.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I love my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:51.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirino, let's make up right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.81,0:21:53.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.94,0:22:00.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This wasn't the time to be fighting about something as silly as what's filthy or disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:03.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry I never realized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:07.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from her, you freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.98,0:22:10.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... who?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:12.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Don't talk, you freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.63,0:22:14.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the root of all the evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.72,0:22:17.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever touch my best friend again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:20.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.80,0:22:22.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.98,0:22:26.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Kirino.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.92,0:22:32.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as planned.{Just as keikaku? TL note: Keikaku means plan.}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.98,0:22:47.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Lying Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:22:50.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your pervertedness has allowed me and Kirino to make up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.06,0:22:55.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you do anything indecent to Kirino, I will beat you to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.64,0:23:02.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.61,0:23:03.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:06.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't done anything you have to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.12,0:23:10.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Ayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.73,0:23:12.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,See you at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:14.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.86,0:23:18.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning to just keep my computer?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.63,0:23:20.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.03,0:23:22.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring it to your room later, happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.37,0:23:24.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.35,0:23:28.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.53,0:23:29.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.61,0:23:32.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to kick your butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,< Preview >
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.21,0:24:06.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Comment: 0,0:24:06.24,0:24:09.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's No Way My Childhood Friend Could Be This Cute
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.87,0:00:08.00,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,そんな優しくしないで　どんな顔すればいいの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:16.80,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,積み重ねた言葉で　見えないよ　きみの横顔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.31,0:00:30.53,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,どこだっけ？　なくした鍵は見つからないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.53,0:00:37.28,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,ため息　すれ違いに意地張って　疲れちゃう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:43.91,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,ほんの少し近く　きみとの距離が
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.91,0:00:51.17,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,うまく掴めないんだ　あとちょっとなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.17,0:00:58.14,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,そんな優しくしないで　ほらまた傷つけあって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.14,0:01:05.14,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,積み重ねた嘘でも　動けなくなってる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.14,0:01:12.57,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,すぐに合いに行きたいけど　言葉は見つからないし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.57,0:01:22.75,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,最後の一ページかい？　きみには笑顔見せたい
Comment: 0,0:01:22.75,0:01:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Romaji}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.87,0:00:08.00,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,sonna yasashiku shinai de donna kao sureba ii no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:16.80,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,tsumikasaneta kotoba de mienaiyo kimi no yokogao
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.31,0:00:30.53,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,dokodakke? nakushita kagi ha mitsukaranai mama de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.53,0:00:37.28,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,tameiki surechigai ni iji hatte tsukarechau
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:43.91,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,hon no sukoshi chikaku kimi to no kyori ga
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.91,0:00:51.17,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,umaku tsukamenainda ato chotto na no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.17,0:00:58.14,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,sonna yasashikushinaide hora mata kizutsukeatte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.14,0:01:05.14,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,tsumikasaneta uso demo ugokenakunatteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.14,0:01:12.57,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,sugu ni ai ni ikitai kedo kotoba ha mitsukaranai shi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.57,0:01:22.75,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,saigo no ichi pe-ji kai? kimi ni ha egao misetai
Comment: 0,0:00:00.04,0:00:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Translation}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.87,0:00:08.00,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so nice to me, I just don't know how to react
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:16.80,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,With all these words piling up, I can't even see your face
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.31,0:00:30.53,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it? I lost my key, now I can't find it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.53,0:00:37.28,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Sigh, I'll burn out if I keep acting like this whenever we miss
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:43.91,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we're close? I just can't figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.91,0:00:51.17,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how far away I am, even though you're right there
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.17,0:00:58.14,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so nice to me, see? We hurt each other again
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.14,0:01:05.14,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,With all these lies piling up, I can't even move
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.14,0:01:12.57,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you now, but I don't know what to say
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.57,0:01:22.75,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the end for our story? I want you to see my smile
