Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:37.52,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,hoshi sae nemuru mayonaka no niji
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.52,0:23:44.36,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,dare mo ienai himitsu no jikan
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.36,0:23:49.43,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,ashita no asayakezora no orenji
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.43,0:23:54.50,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,kitto atashi no kami to onaji
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.50,0:23:57.91,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,itsuka donna kimochi wo wakariaeru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.91,0:24:03.87,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,sonna hito ga dekitara ii na
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:37.52,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,星さえ眠る真夜中の二時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.52,0:23:44.36,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,誰にも言えない秘密の時間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.36,0:23:49.43,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,明日の朝焼け空のオレンジ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.43,0:23:54.50,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,きっとあたしの髪と同じ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.50,0:23:57.91,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,いつかどんな気持ちを分かり合える
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.91,0:24:03.87,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,そんな人ができたらいいな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:37.52,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Two in the morning, the stars are all asleep
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.52,0:23:44.36,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking about a secret I can't tell
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.36,0:23:49.43,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky tomorrow at sunrise will be orange
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.43,0:23:54.50,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it'll be just like my hair
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.50,0:23:57.91,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,How nice if one day I can find
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.91,0:24:03.87,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who'll understand me
